{"tid":1189302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雨傘之後已經唔想再上街抗議","createTime":"2019-06-06T17:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T06:58:50.000Z","uid":41093,"like":76,"dislike":333,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"fe9eb414daa12497e9c126477e5426bc283ba944","tid":1189302,"uid":41093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:25:37.000Z","msg":"5年前上街出一分力，喺金鐘瞓左幾晚。果陣幫手派下工具 野食，搬下水馬，擋左幾粒催淚彈。結果係爭取唔到真普選，外國報道哂雨傘都係無幫忙，畀老果輩話蠢，信果班收咗錢搞亂香港嘅人，畀商人話阻街阻到生意，最後梁天琦都坐埋監<br />\n我都知而家好需要團結，但係心入面始終覺得香港人好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  事不關己己不勞心之餘 仲要扮醒笑9行動果班人<br />\n巴打點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0fd8234f4fb5c48c8abc7bace85c74b13bdd19","tid":1189302,"uid":206594,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:27:07.000Z","msg":"有咩事當去到照應下啲朋友囉<br />\n我都唔信有咩改變或者抗爭模式會變到<br />\n不過真係萬一有突發事<br />\n你有齊乾淨紙巾同水，都幫到唔少人"},{"pid":"e3fd72167c14c631e665fe9bc8cc98b6c7cfdf6f","tid":1189302,"uid":79789,"like":56,"dislike":7,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"fe9eb414daa12497e9c126477e5426bc283ba944","tid":1189302,"uid":41093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:25:37.000Z","msg":"5年前上街出一分力，喺金鐘瞓左幾晚。果陣幫手派下工具 野食，搬下水馬，擋左幾粒催淚彈。結果係爭取唔到真普選，外國報道哂雨傘都係無幫忙，畀老果輩話蠢，信果班收咗錢搞亂香港嘅人，畀商人話阻街阻到生意，最後梁天琦都坐埋監<br />\n我都知而家好需要團結，但係心入面始終覺得香港人好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  事不關己己不勞心之餘 仲要扮醒笑9行動果班人<br />\n巴打點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:28:13.000Z","msg":"巴打 你講得岩 但我問你 <br />\n你 唔去 會唔會後悔<br />\n我估巴打你心入面有答案<br />\n就算無好結果都好 至少我地真係努力過呀!<br />\n而家唔係真唔真普選啦!<br />\n係香港存亡之秋...<br />\n有我地陪你 唔洗理班老野 佢地無未來 佢地唔會CARE"},{"pid":"9e31579b4036ca0ca3c16de333188b0f98f8782a","tid":1189302,"uid":77199,"like":20,"dislike":49,"score":-29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:29:18.000Z","msg":"心已淡 親身有經歷過上次既人<br />\n已經無感覺 金鐘同旺角最後變左做開p勝地 <br />\n狗公溝女既地方 再搞一次都無意義"},{"pid":"466932729e954ba297b2dbfaf18d7f950c034aff","tid":1189302,"uid":57566,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:29:39.000Z","msg":"為自己抗爭<br />\n駛鬼理班港豬<br />\nDo the right things"},{"pid":"c9ed62fdfb8c454aaff217919495be343bcd856e","tid":1189302,"uid":40628,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1uYXVTx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1uYXVTx.jpg&h=4312ee21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"626846fbe398826e85d9943573283ecc2f1046c2","tid":1189302,"uid":160619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:32:48.000Z","msg":"班廢老唔講<br />\n你理得班既得利益者"},{"pid":"07e97f8f9c7a28f4c9a8cc08aae696c90f417cfc","tid":1189302,"uid":118516,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:33:33.000Z","msg":"巴打 無論你做咩決定都好 唔好因為人地點點點 所以自己就要點 最重要係問下自己 係咪想條條例過 <br />\n<br />\n係嘅你咪留響屋企無人阻你 <br />\n唔係嘅就出黎 起碼你唔會後悔 唔係為左其他人 只係為左你反對條例而出黎"},{"pid":"309f71ace16bdaf25c9c304355394ae0aebd8d64","tid":1189302,"uid":31261,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:34:41.000Z","msg":"今次可能係你最後一次合法上街<br />\n唔上唔緊要 個屋企係你的你都唔珍惜<br />\n到失去左你唔後悔就OK"},{"pid":"b7d2a20850c169726e2d546fb6be57346022bed0","tid":1189302,"uid":71509,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:39:26.000Z","msg":"如果69唔出黎<br />\n冇錯⋯ 你可以笑人on9<br />\n食下花生， 好好休息<br />\n<br />\n不過你有可能後悔一世<br />\n因為你再冇機會<br />\n表達自己既意見<br />\n<br />\n我都歸隊啦， 自雨傘後冇出過黎<br />\n<br />\n果種冇力感， 我都明<br />\n<br />\n928係金鐘坐左成晚<br />\n<br />\n全晚都有好多流言傳出黎<br />\n<br />\n每次警犬有舉動， 就叫晒人起身<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後⋯ 我選擇今次歸隊<br />\n<br />\n希望都會見到你"},{"pid":"9e9eba0d8535de2c54897d01085e953d02d5fd70","tid":1189302,"uid":6982,"like":6,"dislike":13,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:39:35.000Z","msg":"心淡了<br />\n個陣已經講今次唔得就再冇下次<br />\n上次嘅失敗根本係群眾自己內部瓦解<br />\n如果冧人堆就得 上次就得左啦<br />\n依家再搞一次同樣嘅野唔會成功"},{"pid":"e8349aaafc192cd490f16a7decfe5a64aaa153a1","tid":1189302,"uid":145923,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:40:12.000Z","msg":"大是大非，唔係訓幾晚，衝幾下就一定改變到。六四時幾多人連命都無埋。都係一樣徒勞無功。唔能夠堅持自己既理念，又認為一定要有用先去做，咁就真係可以唔洗去。<br />\n<br />\n利申：未決定去不去69"},{"pid":"2aab972f2fd4181898d679a74b1e08da9e05b727","tid":1189302,"uid":245484,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:43:55.000Z","msg":"69一定唔出<br />\n頂得到6月10朝早就出去接力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26ea18a550147f258bb18d1f354583fd89cd074","tid":1189302,"uid":226955,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:47:30.000Z","msg":"十個消極撚九個出自波台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e7aa005c4295d8f7a30395ced069d50257ad63","tid":1189302,"uid":226955,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:47:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />事關香港歷史之重大變局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我想借大家少少位用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家可以原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jOPvJL6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjOPvJL6.png&h=344452d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">阻止惡法！為時未晚！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留意返由於預計示威人數好多，民陣已經將起點改咗喺維園！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n<br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n<br />\n集合地點：<span style=\"color: red;\">銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）</span><br />\n<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n<br />\n遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n百國聯軍助陣！感謝海外港人為香港人嘅未來而作出嘅努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AG0SmhW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAG0SmhW.png&h=5d5fe630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>愛因斯坦 (Albert Einstein)：「The world will not be destoryed by those who do evil, but by these who watch them without doing anything.(這個世界不會被那些作惡多端的人毀滅，而是冷眼旁觀、選擇保持緘默的人)」；鄭有傑(導演):「良心的沉默是邪惡的幫兇。」<br />\n<br />\n好多時歷史中嘅轉折位都係由表面上微不足道嘅小事/小人物而形成嘅，所以我地更加唔可以睇小自己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n好重要所以要講三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8ezcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=96ae7e32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（全球聯署、白宮聯署、學界、各行各業、宗教、地區/ 海外港人等等）反送中聯署合集<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY/htmlview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY%2Fhtmlview&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8ezcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=63c1b210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY/htmlview</a>"},{"pid":"07e2b5265b8acec8614744d1c98af4bb856d7de1","tid":1189302,"uid":10757,"like":